                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                      <note>- In<ref type="mss" corresp="ESakm004">AKM-004</ref>α, the miracles are 15 (<locus target="1ra">1ra</locus> – 11vb, 13ra – 16vb), and they are numbered. The miracles 1- 2 are missing and the miracles 7-8 are misplaced, as well as part of the miracles 6 and 9.</note>
                     <note>In the present condition of the manuscript, the actual order of the Miracles is as follows:</note>
                     <note>Miracle 3 (?): <locus target="1ra">1ra</locus> - 2va (l.8), beginning missing;</note>
                     <note>Miracle 4 (፬): <locus target="2va">2va</locus> (l.8) - 3ra (l.12);</note>
                     <note>Miracle 5 (፭): <locus target="3ra">3ra</locus> (l.13) - rb (l.16);</note>
                     <note>Miracle 6 (፮): <locus target="3rb">3rb</locus> (l.16) - 3vb, end misplaced (in <locus target="13ra">13ra</locus> – rb [l.9], s. below);</note>
                     <note>Miracle 9 (፱): <locus target="4ra">4ra</locus> - va (l.8), beginning and part of text misplaced (in <locus target="14ra">14ra</locus> [l.15] – 16vb, s. below);</note>
                     <note>Miracle 10 (፲): <locus target="4va">4va</locus> (l.9) - 5va (l.1);</note>
                     <note>Miracle 11 (፲፩): <locus target="5va">5va</locus> (l.2) - 6vb (l.2);</note>
                     <note>Miracle 12 (፲፪): <locus target="6vb">6vb</locus> (l.2) - 7vb (l.9);</note>
                     <note>Miracle 13 (፲፫): <locus target="7rb">7rb</locus> (l.9) - 8vb (l.4);</note>
                     <note>Miracle 14 (፲፬): <locus target="8vb">8vb</locus> (l.15) - 9vb (l.13);</note>
                     <note>Miracle 15 (፲፭): <locus target="9vb">9vb</locus> (l.14) -10va (l.12);</note>
                     <note>Miracle 16 (፲፮): <locus target="10va">10va</locus> (l.13) - 11ra (l.6);</note>
                     <note>Miracle 17 (፲፯): <locus target="11ra">11ra</locus> (l.7) - 11vb;</note>
                     <note>Miracle 6 (፮):13ra - rb (l.9), beginning misplaced (in <locus target="3rb">3rb</locus> [l.16] - 3vb, s. above);</note>
                     <note>Miracle 7 (፯): <locus target="13rb">13rb</locus> (l.9) - 13vb;</note>
                     <note>Miracle 8 (፰): <locus target="14ra">14ra</locus> (ls. 1-15);</note>
                     <note>Miracle 9 (፱): <locus target="14ra">14ra</locus> (l.15) - 16vb, the end misplaced (in <locus target="4ra">4ra</locus> -va [l.8], s. above).</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>- In<ref type="mss" corresp="ESakm004">AKM-004</ref>β both texts are incomplete and many leaves are misplaced.</note>
                     <note>The Miracles of Text II (<locus target="52va">52va</locus> - 54vb, 57rv) are four; they are not numbered. In the present condition of the manuscript, the order is as follows:</note>
                     <note>Miracle 1: <locus target="52va">52va</locus> - 54vb, end missing;</note>
                     <note>Miracle 2: <locus target="57ra">57ra</locus> (ls.1-18), mostly incomplete, only the end is present;</note>
                     <note>Miracle 3: <locus target="57ra">57ra</locus> (l.18) - 57va (l.16);</note>
                     <note>Miracle 4: <locus target="57va">57va</locus> (l.17) - vb, mostly incomplete.</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>
                        <locus target="55rv">55rv</locus>, 56rv, 58rv, containing part of Text I (Gadla Libānos “Vita of Libānos”: <locus target="12rv">12rv</locus>, 17ra – 52rb, 55ra – 56vb57ra [l.18], 58rv), are misplaced. <locus target="58rv">58rv</locus> contains the incipit of Text I.</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>- For the Texts of Gadla Libānos, Taʾāmra Libānos and Malkǝʾa Libānos compare them to the edited version: A. BAUSI, La «Vita» e i «miracoli» di Libānos, Lovanii 2003 (CSCO 595, 596 [SAe 105, 106]).</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>- In<ref type="mss" corresp="ESakm004">AKM-004</ref>γ, the text is incomplete and partly misplaced.</note>
                     <note>According to the edition P. LEANDER, ʼArgānōna Ŭeddāsē, Leipzig 1922,</note>
                     <note>the correct sequence of the folios should be as follows:</note>
                     <note>
                        <locus target="59ra">59ra</locus> - 60vb: Sat. LVIII, p. 165, l.9 - p. 167, <locus target="10">10</locus>;</note>
                     <note>
                        <locus target="62ra">62ra</locus> - 63vb: Sat. LVIII, p. 167, l.11 - p. 169, l.8;</note>
                     <note>
                        <locus target="61rv">61rv</locus>: Sat. LVIII, p. 169, ls. 8-19.</note>
                     <note>Part of the text in <locus target="59rv">59rv</locus> is missing due to the present condition of the leaf (it is mutilated at bottom side),</note>
                     <note>
                        <locus target="61">61</locus> is misplaced and the text in <locus target="61v">61v</locus> is incomplete (lacuna in column b); in the same folio the list of names from ls. 6-16 is different from the edited version (s. above).</note>
